{"tid":692372,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[LIHKG]動漫台緣份計劃意見及人口調查　","createTime":"2018-06-06T14:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T07:57:32.000Z","uid":176045,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1f36cb649f96a9965c6937ffb2c7b44ebaae6339","tid":692372,"uid":176045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"<del>在動漫台尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麼?</del><br />\n<br />\n大家好，小弟有意係LIHKG搞只屬於動漫台既緣份計劃，比大家認識興趣相近既異性或同性啦。<br />\n想大家花小小時間填份問卷比意見，睇下可唔可行，多唔多人參與。如果過半數反對我自己收皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外，仲想做個人口調查，統計大家瀏覽動漫台既習慣。個人對動漫台既生態圈好有興趣，希望兩星期內整到個報告比大家。<br />\n歡迎大家提出唔同既意見<del>/狠評</del>，感謝各位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問卷調查Link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2Fe6Plh03iiQCCX5p73&d=kV2Lz1FzZgpehjoPeQXrLU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=746052d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/e6Plh03iiQCCX5p73</a><br />\n<br />\nReference: <br />\n好宅之人 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fveryotaku&d=kV2Lz1FzZgpehjoPeQXrLU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=50037fff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/veryotaku</a><br />\n緣份配對計劃 <a href=\"https://matchup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatchup.hk&d=kV2Lz1FzZgpehjoPeQXrLU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=2c030163\" target=\"_blank\">https://matchup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"b20b5bfd19487232a9622ae014fb48691f47fd3e","tid":692372,"uid":147871,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"168男 85kg<br />\n鐘意環遊世界<br />\n想識絲打<br />\n有誠意既留tg 我會揀黎覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/231433_60eeab171836cb621b301ccdff5565cd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu